{
  "texts": [
    "Results validated that GPT-4 used more complex language compared to humans and that language complexity predicted reappraisal quality for both groups in conjunction.",
    "Finally, to get a more qualitative evaluation of the differences between humans and GPT-4 reappraisals, we tried to isolate the words that were uniquely used by either GPT-4 or humans.",
    "We were able to isolate words that were characteristic for GPT-4 and humans such that we can predict the source of reappraisal using these words.",
    "We also show that when words that are more characteristic of GPT-4 reappraisals are used by humans, the reappraisals are considered higher quality.",
    "These results, discussed in detail below, provide more information on the differences between human and GPT-4 reappraisals / responses."
  ]
}